9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:56,144 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 23=

11
00:01:06,719 --> 00:01:08,760
The Heavenly Dao has come.

12
00:01:11,719 --> 00:01:13,159
Take Ningxue and go.

13
00:01:14,120 --> 00:01:16,760
I'll face the Heavenly Dao alone.

14
00:01:17,239 --> 00:01:18,120
Futile.

15
00:01:18,159 --> 00:01:20,000
Defy the laws all you want,

16
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:23,120
your ending is already decided.

17
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:25,000
The Heavenly Dao?

18
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:26,120
Law?

19
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:29,239
Why must you torment Ningxue
again and again?

20
00:01:29,439 --> 00:01:31,920
It's not torment. It's return.

21
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:34,359
Life must return to the universe.

22
00:01:34,359 --> 00:01:36,239
That is the eternal law.

23
00:01:36,959 --> 00:01:38,280
What a load of nonsense!

24
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:39,920
Her life belongs to her.

25
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:42,000
Not to Heaven. And certainly not to you.

26
00:01:42,159 --> 00:01:44,040
If the Heavenly Dao wants her dead,

27
00:01:44,439 --> 00:01:46,239
then you're the one I should deal with!

28
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,199
Ningxue!

29
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,240
Wubing. Catch this!

30
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,560
What a load of nonsense!

31
00:02:52,159 --> 00:02:55,520
Her life belongs to her.

32
00:02:58,599 --> 00:03:00,080
Not to Heaven. And certainly not to you.

33
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,599
In this life,

34
00:03:11,599 --> 00:03:12,719
I'll stand with you

35
00:03:15,759 --> 00:03:16,840
and fight the Heavenly Dao!

36
00:03:54,692 --> 00:03:58,720
ظآزTime cuts like a blade,
severing all desireظآز

37
00:03:58,879 --> 00:03:59,560
Ningxue...

38
00:03:59,604 --> 00:04:01,199
ظآزIn the end,
we fall into an endless tideظآز

39
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:02,000
Ningxue...

40
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,400
ظآزIn the end,
we fall into an endless tideظآز

41
00:04:03,592 --> 00:04:08,200
ظآزIf fate is cruel,
is there anything left?ظآز

42
00:04:08,419 --> 00:04:09,719
ظآزThen let these immortal bones scatterظآز

43
00:04:09,719 --> 00:04:11,199
No, Ningxue!

44
00:04:11,879 --> 00:04:13,000
Ningxue, don't go!

45
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:14,599
Ningxue!

46
00:04:16,110 --> 00:04:17,480
ظآزI defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortalityظآز

47
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:18,000
Ningxue!

48
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,640
ظآزI defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortalityظآز

49
00:04:20,016 --> 00:04:23,079
ظآزJust to meet you again in the crowdظآز

50
00:04:23,079 --> 00:04:23,920
Ten thousand years ago,

51
00:04:25,399 --> 00:04:28,000
you gave everything
to protect me during seclusion.

52
00:04:28,959 --> 00:04:30,160
Ten thousand years later,

53
00:04:31,399 --> 00:04:33,560
even if it costs me everything,

54
00:04:34,879 --> 00:04:36,480
I'll protect you.

55
00:04:38,279 --> 00:04:39,000
Ningxue.

56
00:04:39,297 --> 00:04:41,399
