73
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,279
Su Wubing...

74
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:07,560
My Lord, can you still

75
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:11,120
feel any spiritual power at all?

76
00:06:19,079 --> 00:06:20,480
If it means getting Ningxue back,

77
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,279
living as an ordinary person

78
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,399
is more than fine with me.

79
00:06:24,279 --> 00:06:25,079
What a shame.

80
00:06:25,879 --> 00:06:26,720
Lin Rong.

81
00:06:28,319 --> 00:06:30,920
My Lord gave everything for your family.

82
00:06:31,319 --> 00:06:33,399
You must repay him.

83
00:06:34,199 --> 00:06:34,800
Of course.

84
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:38,240
Wubing has done so much for us.

85
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,319
He saved Ningxue.

86
00:06:40,399 --> 00:06:43,120
We could never fully repay that debt.

87
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:48,600
Wubing, don't worry about

88
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:49,800
your spiritual power.

89
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:53,279
Come to my martial hall from now on.

90
00:06:53,839 --> 00:06:55,839
I'll teach you
the Shan family's techniques.

91
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:58,600
You'll be even stronger than before.

92
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,279
Okay.

93
00:06:59,279 --> 00:07:00,600
No way.

94
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:03,360
He's already engaged to Ningxue.

95
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:05,399
He's part of the Lin family now.

96
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,680
Why not?

97
00:07:06,959 --> 00:07:10,360
I think he and Yingying
are a great match too.

98
00:07:10,959 --> 00:07:11,920
Alright, enough.

99
00:07:13,079 --> 00:07:14,399
My Lord's heart

100
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:19,160
