101
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,439
Stop arguing.

102
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:23,199
Oh, right,

103
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:24,879
where are

104
00:07:25,639 --> 00:07:26,920
