108
00:07:35,519 --> 00:07:36,720
And Yingying too...

109
00:07:37,319 --> 00:07:40,079
Did something happen?

110
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,199
Look... they're here.

111
00:08:06,839 --> 00:08:07,680
- Su Wubing!
- Su Wubing!

112
00:08:14,279 --> 00:08:14,959
Su Wubing.

113
00:08:17,519 --> 00:08:18,160
You all...

114
00:08:19,319 --> 00:08:20,120
Like it?

115
00:08:20,439 --> 00:08:22,600
Wubing, you must choose one of us today.

116
00:08:22,879 --> 00:08:23,519
That's right.

117
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:24,639
Yes.

118
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:28,199
Exactly.

