127
00:10:01,159 --> 00:10:01,679
Got it.

128
00:10:01,759 --> 00:10:02,120
Thanks.

129
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:20,559
You've been asleep so long.

130
00:10:21,559 --> 00:10:23,200
You haven't heard the good news.

131
00:10:26,559 --> 00:10:28,559
(Against Fate)
Look, this is your script.

132
00:10:30,159 --> 00:10:31,440
They loved it.

133
00:10:31,519 --> 00:10:33,600
A lot of people want your autograph.

134
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:44,639
You always used to read to me.

135
00:10:45,159 --> 00:10:47,240
After being asleep so long,
you've probably forgotten.

136
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,360
Let me read it to you now.

137
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:54,480
"Su Wubing finally married Lin Ningxue."

138
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:58,799
"At the wedding, he recalled the past."

139
00:10:59,080 --> 00:11:02,159
"Fate... had finally been broken."

140
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:05,240
"But where does it all lead in the end?"

141
00:11:06,399 --> 00:11:08,279
"The undercurrents in Fan City
haven't stopped."

142
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:10,879
"It looks calm on the surface,"

143
00:11:12,159 --> 00:11:13,879
"but what storms still lie hidden?"

